text: A synth or synthesizer is an electronic musical instrument. Synth may also refer to: __NOTOC__ ==Science== *Synthetic biology *Synthetic intelligence ==Media== * Synth (video game), a freeware strategic action game that utilizes procedurally generated graphics * Synth, machines powered by organic components used by the Combine in the Half-Life video game series * Synth, androids featured in the video game Fallout 4 * Synth, anthropomorphic robots depicted in the television series Humans ==Other uses== * Synth Look and Feel, a skinnable Java look and feel ==See also== *Synthetic (disambiguation) *
